oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Joe F. Manley with 22-lb. muskellunge caught in Little Tennessee River, below Calderwood Dam
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Joe F. Manley with a 22-lb. muskellunge caught in the Little Tennessee River below Calderwood Dam. Manley is standing in front of a vehicle holding up the muskellunge to show the size of the fish. Manley is wearing a button down shirt, necktie and trousers.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
